    @Operator.DependsOn(value={ConvertingCopier.class,NOPConverter.class,ELCoercionConverter.class,DefaultCopyingConverter.class})
public abstract class PropertyCopier<SOURCE,TARGET>
extends Copier<SOURCE,TARGET>
    Copies based on annotations. Concrete subclasses must specify one or both of PropertyCopier.Mapping and PropertyCopier.Matching to designate property/expression (using #{} embedding syntax).
